These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing, hiking, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | rock-climbing | hiking | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, boat, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Transport   | car | bus | motorbike | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, daffodil, sunflower, tulip
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Flower   | rose | sunflower | daffodil | tulip |

