.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
House: victorian, wooden, gothic-revival, futuristic
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
3. the victorian house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| House   | wooden | victorian | futuristic | gothic-revival |

