.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, zombie, romance
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching romance movies##2
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | scientific | animation | zombie |

