2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2     |    3    |  4   |
| Hobby   | skydiving | fishing | sudoku | gardening |

