.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, october, january, november
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Birthday   | january | october | february | november |

 